OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Fsome rain and showers likely during
OL,7,Fthe evening, these becoming
OL,8,Fincreasingly patchy and confined to
OL,9,Fthe Pennines overnight, with some
OL,10,Fcloud breaks developing in the east by
OL,11,Fthe morning. Winds easing overnight.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FEarly cloud and any residual
OL,14,Fpatchy rain, soon clearing to leave a
OL,15,Fgenerally dry and bright day with
OL,16,Fsunny spells later. Temperatures
OL,17,Fslightly lower than previous days.
OL,18,FWinds generally light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
