OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday
OL,6,Fand Monday, mainly dry and fine, just
OL,7,Fa chance of isolated thunderstorms.
OL,8,FTuesday, perhaps cloudier with a
OL,9,Fchance of showers later. Temperatures
OL,10,Fclimbing, likely turning very warm and
OL,11,Fhumid.
